  },
  {
    "start": 12.16,
    "end": 17.95,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "歡迎來到第八十二集熱量計算大公開",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 18.15,
    "end": 21.81,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "老師講義上面的熱量公式",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 22.01,
    "end": 25.16,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "看起來密密麻麻好複雜喔",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 25.36,
    "end": 29.21,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "戰士們別怕其實非常簡單",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 29.41,
    "end": 33.4,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "熱量就是把三個東西全部相乘",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 33.6,
    "end": 37.78,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "質量乘以比熱再乘以溫度變化",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 37.98,
    "end": 98.06,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "$$\\Delta H = M \\times S \\times \\Delta T$$",
    "is_pinned": true,
    "pin_level": 1,
    "commands": [
      "釘選",
      "$$\\Delta H = M \\times S \\times \\Delta T$$"
    ]
  },
  {
    "start": 41.46,
    "end": 44.56,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "那下面熱平衡的計算題",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 44.76,
    "end": 48.42,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "我們到底該怎麼列式子才不會錯",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 48.62,
    "end": 52.32,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "記住一個最重要的熱學大原則",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 52.52,
    "end": 55.65,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "高溫物體放出來的熱量",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 55.85,
    "end": 59.36,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "一定等於低溫物體吸收的熱量",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 59.56,
    "end": 62.78,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "就像哥哥口袋掏出十塊錢",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 62.98,
    "end": 66.47,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "妹妹就剛好收到十塊錢對吧",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 66.67,
    "end": 72.27,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "沒錯假設最後混合的平衡溫度是 $$T$$",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 72.47,
    "end": 76.92,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "高溫減掉平衡溫度 $$T$$就是下降的溫度",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 77.12,
    "end": 81.57,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "平衡溫度 $$T$$ 減掉低溫就是上升的溫度",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 81.77,
    "end": 98.06,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "$$M_1 \\times S_1 \\times (T_1-T) = M_2 \\times S_2 \\times (T-T_2)$$",
    "is_pinned": true,
    "pin_level": 2,
    "commands": [
      "釘選",
      "$$M_1 \\times S_1 \\times (T_1-T) = M_2 \\times S_2 \\times (T-T_2)$$"
    ]
  },
  {
    "start": 86.61,
    "end": 90.89,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "哇只要依照這個邏輯列出來",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 91.09,
    "end": 94.86,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "就可以輕鬆解一元一次方程式了",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 98.06,
    "end": 102.1,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "接著我們來看右下角的溫度時間圖",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 102.3,
    "end": 106.27,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "這可是大考最愛出的必考圖表題",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 106.47,
    "end": 110.1,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "老師圖上有三條斜斜的線",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 110.3,
    "end": 113.14,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "這到底要怎麼比大小啊",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 113.34,
    "end": 117.58,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "戰士們想像你在考場拿出直尺",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 117.78,
    "end": 121.62,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "找個時間點畫一條鉛直線下來",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 121.82,
    "end": 125.74,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "這代表大家的加熱時間一模一樣",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 125.94,
    "end": 129.62,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "也就是吸收的熱量完全一樣多",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 129.82,
    "end": 133.79,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "哇我發現黑色的那條線",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 133.99,
    "end": 137.19,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "它的溫度瞬間衝得最高耶",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 137.39,
    "end": 141.5,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "溫度衝得最快代表它很容易熱",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 141.7,
    "end": 145.43,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "容易熱也就代表它的比熱最小",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 145.63,
    "end": 181.75,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "線越陡 $$\\rightarrow$$ 溫度升得快 $$\\rightarrow$$ 比熱小",
    "is_pinned": true,
    "pin_level": 1,
    "commands": [
      "釘選",
      "線越陡 $$\\rightarrow$$ 溫度升得快 $$\\rightarrow$$ 比熱小"
    ]
  },
  {
    "start": 150.42,
    "end": 153.5,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "那最下面黃色的那條線",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 153.7,
    "end": 156.21,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "溫度上升得最慢",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 156.41,
    "end": 159.3,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "就代表它的比熱最大囉",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 159.5,
    "end": 161.88,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "完全正確",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 162.08,
    "end": 181.75,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "線越平 $$\\rightarrow$$ 溫度升得慢 $$\\rightarrow$$ 比熱大",
    "is_pinned": true,
    "pin_level": 2,
    "commands": [
